# Cards Tracker — Roadmap

Living document. Update as items ship or priorities shift. **Product vision, comp matching, profit targets:** see `product-vision.mdc`.

When the user asks "what next?" or "what are we working on?", reference this + product-vision.

## Now (highest ROI — accuracy first)

### 1. Pricing accuracy + comp match badges (Phase 1 — BLOCKER)
Everything else depends on trustworthy numbers. Full spec in `product-vision.mdc`.

- Fix grade-tier price selection (`pickPriceForGrade` — PSA 9 must not show raw)
- Add `CompMatchLevel` to `PortfolioValuation` + badges on portfolio / watchlist / card detail
- Canonical metadata on add via `lookupCanonicalCard`; backfill existing portfolio rows
- Strict eBay comp filtering (grade + variant + card # in title)
- Honest labels: PC volume vs grade-specific comp count; null trend → "—" not fake %
- Backfill `pricecharting_id` on `price_aggregates`; daily `recompute-trends` pg_cron
- Tests: `lib/parsing/grade.ts`, `pickPriceForGrade`, `lib/card-parser.ts`

### 2. Profit target + "Ready to Sell" (Phase 2a — after Phase 1)
Profile/Settings: user sets target profit % (default 20%, optional net-after-fees).

- Settings: `target_profit_pct`, `profit_includes_fees`, `estimated_sell_fee_pct`
- Portfolio section: cards at target / near target / hold
- Later: push when card crosses target

### 3. Portfolio trading dashboard (Phase 2b)
- `portfolio_snapshots` daily cron + value-over-time chart
- Header: total value, today P/L, cost basis, unrealized gain
- Best/worst performers; formalize `sold_cards` + realized P/L
- CSV export (web first) — **Pro**

### 3b. On-demand price refresh (Phase 2c — ship before Stripe)
- Pull-to-refresh / refresh button on portfolio + card detail
- `fetchPortfolioValuation({ forceRefresh: true })` bypasses 30min client cache
- Server quota: e.g. 3/day free (`valuation_refresh_log`); show "N left today"
- Pro = unlimited (flag only until payment)
- See `product-vision.mdc` → Monetization

### 4. Notifications & alerts
- `expo-notifications` + `notification_preferences` table
- Watchlist target hit; portfolio ≥X% move; profit target crossed; daily digest
- Supabase scheduled edge function for diffs

## Next

### 5. Smarter scanning
- Slab label OCR for grade; front/back fusion; "Did you mean…?"; bulk scan; cert barcode

### 6. Discover & deals
- Undervalued vs comps; saved searches; auctions ending soon

### 7. Card detail upgrades
- Grade tier comparison (Raw / PSA 9 / PSA 10); PSA pop; real trend reasons

### 8. Gamification (Phase 3 — after accuracy)
- Milestone toasts, streaks, confetti on gains, daily digest copy

## Later

### 9. Social / community
Public profiles, follow collectors, comments, leaderboards.

### 10. Polish & infra
Offline cache, skeleton loaders, settings (theme, currency), Sentry, tests expansion.

### 11. Monetization (Pro)
Free: accurate valuations on load, limited refresh, 50 portfolio / 10 watchlist.
Pro: unlimited refresh, alerts, CSV, bulk scan, full chart history, grade-tier compare.
See full matrix in `product-vision.mdc`. **Implement quotas before payment integration.**

### 12. M3 Expressive UI
Experimental preview at `/m3-home` — promote only after core product is trustworthy.

